Use the standard library
This is how to is_sorted of lst:
  When lst's length is at most 1, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this lst's length times:
    When i is at least lst's length, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When item i in lst is less than item diff of i and 1 in lst, then:
      The answer is 0
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is 1
